{"word":"G2638 - καταλαμβάνω - katalambánō - kat-al-am-ban'-o - Apprehend","slug":"G2638","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταλαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katalambánō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-al-am-ban'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Apprehend"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03BC;&#x03B2;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - katalambano&#x0304;</b> - <i>kat-al-am-ban'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G1983\">G1983</a>; to <i>take eagerly</i>, that is, <i>seize</i>, <i>possess</i>, etc. (literally or figuratively): - apprehend, attain, come upon, comprehend, find, obtain, perceive, (over-) take."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274\">G5274</a>"}]}